      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/eced774c193e995be610f4d77e9b1f1e56498a1d.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=54b5bf2c9779e9d14a8e732f330da16c"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/772fda3fe1889a8d1ee2d6b5ac4c57c2421fc14b.png?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=2fe42c708dc30585d1d52b7999ef5e96"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Live in the clouds with AWS &amp; Azure&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Become a 21st-century superstar with the latest Humble Tech Book Bundle: Cloud Infrastructure and DevOps Toolkit. Learn the intricacies of Amazon Web Services with industry-leading courses like &lt;em&gt;AWS for Solutions Architects&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;AWS Cloud Projects&lt;/em&gt;—master Microsoft Azure with professional-quality lessons like &lt;em&gt;Hands-On MLOps on Azure&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;Azure for Developers&lt;/em&gt;. This comprehensive library includes lessons, practice tests, and resources perfect for novices and seasoned professionals alike—build strong foundations in cloud infrastructure and help support No Kid Hungry with your purchase.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#cloudnativeanti-patterns"&gt;Cloud Native Anti-Patterns&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sustainableclouddevelopment"&gt;Sustainable Cloud Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#ciandcddesignpatterns"&gt;CI/CD Design Patterns&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt12"&gt;Pay $12 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#kubernetesbible"&gt;The Kubernetes Bible&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#self-taughtcloudcomputingengineer"&gt;The Self-Taught Cloud Computing Engineer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#ultimatedockercontainerbookthirdedition"&gt;The Ultimate Docker Container Book&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt18"&gt;Pay $18 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#solutionsarchitectshandbookthirdedition"&gt;Solutions Architect's Handbook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#platformengineeringforarchitects"&gt;Platform Engineering for Architects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#examrefaz-104microsoftazureadministratorcertificationandbeyond"&gt;Exam Ref AZ-104 Microsoft Azure Administrator Certification and Beyond&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#microsoftazurefundamentalscertificationandbeyondsecondedition"&gt;Microsoft Azure Fundamentals Certification and Beyond&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#kubernetesforgenerativeaisolutions"&gt;Kubernetes for Generative AI Solutions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#awsforsolutionsarchitects"&gt;AWS for Solutions Architects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#masteringenterpriseplatformengineering"&gt;Mastering Enterprise Platform Engineering&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#azurecloudprojects"&gt;Azure Cloud Projects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#handsonmlopsonazure"&gt;Hands-On MLOps on Azure&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#developingsolutionsformicrosoftazureaz-204examguide"&gt;Developing Solutions for Microsoft Azure AZ-204 Exam Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildingresilientarchitecturesonaws"&gt;Building Resilient Architectures on AWS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#awscertifiedsolutionsarchitectstudyguidewith900practicetestquestio"&gt;AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Associate (SAA-C03) Exam Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#awscloudprojects"&gt;AWS Cloud Projects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#implementinggitopswithkubernetes"&gt;Implementing GitOps with Kubernetes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#azurefordevelopers"&gt;Azure for Developers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="cloudnativeanti-patterns"&gt;&lt;a id="cloudnativeanti-patterns" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/cloudnativeanti-patterns_preview.pdf?t=st=1757175439~exp=1757261839~hmac=7f7a160054e14f62635962f77485c8e2b131fa21eeeded5e2400f9d73d38faf3"&gt;Cloud Native Anti-Patterns&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/15cd029487d28656626e3f0b827471743cd44b7d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7c43a56ae35bf719663736aff3cd9d81"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Key Features&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Identify common anti-patterns in agile cloud-native delivery and learn to adopt good habits&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Learn high-performing cloud-native delivery with expert strategies and real-world examples&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Get prescriptive guidance on how to spot and remediate anti-patterns in your organization&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Purchase of the print or Kindle book includes a free PDF eBook&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Who this book is for&lt;/h4&gt;This book is for cloud professionals with any level of experience who want to deepen their knowledge and guide their organization toward cloud-native success. It is Ideal for cloud architects, engineers (cloud, software, data, or network), cloud security experts, technical leaders, and cloud operations personnel. While no specific expertise is required, a background in architecture, software development, data, networks, operations, or governance will be helpful.&lt;h3 id="sustainableclouddevelopment"&gt;&lt;a id="sustainableclouddevelopment" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/sustainableclouddevelopment_preview.pdf?t=st=1757175439~exp=1757261839~hmac=6f4ff3a2a011aeadd81fd2fbe1df81b9eb259d1618217e9be6ebd652872867fd"&gt;Sustainable Cloud Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/22b11e2a237891dde626a5690d5762e7f856b9d3.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=393c9958bd106b1f8e08f296c2a19870"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Key Features&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Discover sustainable cloud practices, including carbon footprint analysis, optimization, and security&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Explore best practices, insights, and case studies for implementing sustainable solutions like generative AI workloads&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Learn cost-saving strategies through efficient resource use and business alignment&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Purchase of the print or Kindle book includes a free PDF eBook&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Who this book is for&lt;/h4&gt;This book is for cloud architects, engineers, DevOps professionals, and IT sustainability specialists who want to align their cloud practices with environmental goals. It also caters to software developers eager to build green, efficient solutions. A basic understanding of cloud services and IT infrastructure is necessary.&lt;h3 id="ciandcddesignpatterns"&gt;&lt;a id="ciandcddesignpatterns" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/ciandcddesignpatterns_preview.pdf?t=st=1757175439~exp=1757261839~hmac=f585e29807f18369b9ef195dd55224e140aa96101b1fc7136db8a99471315f88"&gt;CI/CD Design Patterns&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9db9320631e2d85704478fdc5e0d23dad0cdc094.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c0fdd2a6f164ee3e4059f3ac0e464bd5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Key Features&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Simplify CI/CD adoption with the help of practical examples, case studies, and best practices&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Deploy market-ready solutions by implementing key components like pipelines, infrastructure, and release capabilities&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Explore advanced design patterns, including integration with machine learning and generative AI&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Purchase of the print or Kindle book includes a free PDF eBook&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Who this book is for&lt;/h4&gt;This design patterns book is for senior software developers, software architects, SRE architects, DevOps architects, cloud architects and platform engineering teams looking to speed up the development process by adopting well-tested, proven development/design paradigms for continuous delivery and its adoption. You are expected to have a basic understanding of CI/CD concepts and be familiar with the cloud ecosystem, DevOps principles, and CI/CD pipelines.&lt;h2 id="bt12"&gt;Pay $12 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="kubernetesbible"&gt;&lt;a id="kubernetesbible" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/kubernetesbible_preview.pdf?t=st=1757175439~exp=1757261839~hmac=b1786d9ff9ab4867888f5b789084777b96124685bbebe692e1f720314cb3f736"&gt;The Kubernetes Bible&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/df8f2271fd7ec456caa55aa592f19f5c8cdc80b6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=985304cb074d8a78299012e9052e79d5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Key Features&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive coverage of Kubernetes concepts - from deployment to   cluster and resource management&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Gain insights into the latest cloud-native trends and how they impact your Kubernetes deployments&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tap into the collective wisdom of acclaimed Kubernetes experts&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Who this book is for&lt;/h4&gt;Whether you're a software developer, DevOps engineer, or an existing Kubernetes user, this Kubernetes book   is your comprehensive guide to mastering container orchestration and services in the cloud. It empowers you to overcome challenges in building secure, scalable, and cloud-native applications using Kubernetes. With a foundational understanding of Kubernetes, Docker, and leading cloud providers (AWS, Azure, GCP) recommended, this book equips you with the knowledge and skills needed to  navigate complex deployments and master core Kubernetes concepts and architecture.&lt;h3 id="self-taughtcloudcomputingengineer"&gt;&lt;a id="self-taughtcloudcomputingengineer" href="https://cdn.humble