&gt;Windows: (Yes)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mac: (Yes)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Console: (Yes)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="modularmedievalfortressmegapackfabprofessionallicensekey"&gt;&lt;a id="modularmedievalfortressmegapackfabprofessionallicensekey" href="https://youtu.be/G0I2gvlL0oU"&gt;Modular Medieval Fortress Megapack (FAB Professional License Key)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Check It Out On Fab Marketplace &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/826f1b55-01e2-4272-993d-ea142a264f9f"&gt;Here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*Professional Fab Marketplace Key is provided!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UE5 - The map was made specifically for UE5 using Lumen and nanite to drastically enhance visuals and performance!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enterable - All buildings are fully enterable and ready to be populated with your favorite assets! (Door mechanic working out of the box)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fully Modular - Enjoy a fully modular kit to create your own medieval environments with ease. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Massive - With over 334 meshes, 290 materials/material instances and 454 textures in your disposal you'll have a variety of new meshes and materials to play with to create an endless amount of towns and cities!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VFX Library - A vast VFX library including spline based birds, bats, insects, butterflies, water FX, Fire FX are included!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Easy Sky - A powerful cloud tool is included (Used to create the clouds behind the castle) create vast cloud systems in under a minute!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Light Beam - A lighting artist's best friend our light beam blueprint is an easy solution to instantly add a dramatic flair to any scene!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Day/Night Scene - Pack contains two bespoke lighting setups one a classic dramatic day light theme while the other an eerie night scene!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 334&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collision: (Yes automatically generated)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vertex Count: 75 - 27,000&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LODs: (Yes)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 290&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Number of Textures: 454&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Texture Resolutions: (512x512, 1024x1024, 2048x2048)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supported Development Platforms:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Windows: (Yes)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mac: (Yes)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Console: (Yes)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="modularruraltownandruralvillagefabprofessionallicensekey"&gt;&lt;a id="modularruraltownandruralvillagefabprofessionallicensekey" href="https://youtu.be/dkH0l2n18o8"&gt;Modular Rural Town / Rural Village (FAB Professional License Key)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Check It Out On Fab Marketplace &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/27739a61-d46d-4bd9-826a-1005c8dbd30b"&gt;Here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*Professional Fab Marketplace Key is provided!&lt;/st