process of building, training, and deploying custom machine learning models with Amazon SageMaker.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Explore the world of Generative AI on AWS, learning to build applications with foundation models using Amazon Bedrock.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Leverage AWS's pre-trained AI services for vision, language, and forecasting to quickly add intelligence to applications.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This program is designed for developers, data analysts, and solutions architects who want to gain a comprehensive understanding of how to build and deploy AI/ML solutions on AWS.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Includes a comprehensive library of 20 full-length practice exams. Master the AWS AI/ML services. Build with confidence on the cloud.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you're ready to build the next generation of intelligent applications and unlock your career potential on the AWS cloud, your training starts now.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="azure_aiengineer_microsoftcert_10practiceexams"&gt;&lt;a id="azure_aiengineer_microsoftcert_10practiceexams"&gt;Get Microsoft Certified as an Azure AI Engineer Associate with 10 Practice Exams&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/90422be445ebf214a155442b81748e97b48235bf.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=12e112df01ba7ed8fe647b74d43b9671"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;You don't have to be a data scientist to build powerful AI solutions. This program teaches you how to use Microsoft Azure's pre-built AI services to infuse your applications with advanced capabilities for vision, speech, language, and search.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course prepares you for the Azure AI Engineer Associate exam by covering how to design and implement solutions using Azure AI Services, Azure OpenAI Service, and Azure AI Search.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Learn to implement solutions that analyze images (Vision), recognize and synthesize speech (Speech), and process natural language (Language).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Build applications using the Azure OpenAI Service to leverage powerful generative models for content creation and summarization.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Create intelligent knowledge mining solutions with Azure AI Search to enable semantic search over your organization's data.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Understand how to plan and manage an Azure AI solution, including security, monitoring, and deployment to production.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course is designed for software developers and engineers who want to expand their skills by building AI-powered applications on the Microsoft Azure platform.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Includes 10 full-length practice exams. Solidify your understanding of Azure AI Services. Engineer intelligent solutions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you're ready to move beyond traditional development and start building the next generation of smart applications, this course is your API to the future.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="databricks_dataanalystassociate_10practiceexams"&gt;&lt;a id="databricks_dataanalystassociate_10practiceexams"&gt;Databricks Certified Data Analyst Associate Exam Preparation with 10 Practice Exams&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1fef3a887376f69802b538f12401747bb768f907.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ef0ded10fdd22c409cbb2eb683dc673c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unleash the power of your SQL skills on the massive scale of the Databricks Lakehouse. This program teaches you how to use the familiar language of SQL to query petabytes of data and build powerful analytics dashboards.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master the tools and techniques for data analysis and visualization on the Databricks platform, learning how to write efficient SQL queries, manage query performance, and build insightful dashboards.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Learn to navigate the Databricks SQL environment, manage SQL warehouses for optimal performance, and understand the Lakehouse architecture.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Understand how to work with data objects in the Lakehouse, including creating and managing tables, views, and using Unity Catalog for governance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Write sophisticated SQL queries to analyze data, including working with complex data types, advanced functions, and window functions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Develop insightful visualizations and build interactive dashboards directly within Databricks to share your findings with stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course is designed for data analysts, BI professionals, and anyone with strong SQL skills who wants to perform analytics on the Databricks Lakehouse platform.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Includes 10 full-length practice exams. Sharpen your SQL skills. Analyze with clarity and speed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you're ready to use your analytical skills to unlock insights from big data and empower data-driven decisions, this course is your query plan.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="comptia_dataplus_10practiceexams"&gt;&lt;a id="comptia_dataplus_10practiceexams"&gt;CompTIA Data+ with 10 Practice Exams&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/58c00eaa94002e1e2aad63c65fa74d124d63c063.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=eda011e4e9afdad50283c10c38f55e7f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Every dataset tells a story. The challenge is knowing how to find it and how to tell it effectively. This program teaches you the complete data analysis lifecycle, from mining raw data to visualizing compelling insights.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master the foundational skills of a data analyst, learning how to source and manipulate data, apply basic statistical methods, and create meaningful visualizations to communicate results.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Understand core data concepts, different data types, and the importance of data governance and quality.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Learn techniques for data mining and manipulation, including how to query and transform data for analysis.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Explore the application of descriptive statistics and basic analytical techniques to uncover patterns in data.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Master the principles of effective data visualization and learn how to build reports that clearly communicate insights.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're an aspiring analyst seeking your first role or a professional who needs to make data-driven decisions, this course provides the vendor-neutral, foundational skills to succeed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Includes 10 full-length practice exams. Solidify your understanding of the analysis process. Prepare with confidence.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you're ready to build the essential skills for a career in data and learn how to turn numbers into narrative, this course is your first chapter.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="comptia_techplus_10practiceexams"&gt;&lt;a id="comptia_techplus_10practiceexams"&gt;CompTIA Tech+ Complete Certification Exam Preparation with 10 Practice Exams&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/aac6209d45f2050a2c6d478c3c37c5620b009fb9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=763e56d1ccec7283f09c54f8828bbd75"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Every journey into a career in technology starts with a single, solid foundation. This is it. This program teaches you the essential, universal skills in hardware, software, networking, and security that every IT professional needs to know.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Gain the core, hands-on knowledge to support modern IT infrastructure, from assembling hardware and configuring operating systems to troubleshooting network and security issues.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Identify, install, and troubleshoot PC hardware and peripherals, and learn to manage common operating systems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Understand the fundamentals of networking, including TCP/IP, common protocols, and how to configure network connections.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Grasp essential cybersecurity principles, including identifying threats, implementing access controls, and securing data.&l