      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5f4c6d1207ce2dedddaf4e081d343a63c22ed592.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=5ca39405abef518fc2526e6a14db59d4"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9a9dc3509c23f6e3a623a7f5edba6fecf4ac4af5.png?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=8b89b005db7e167f3beaabf6dd1e7439"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Learn endlessly with Skillademia&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Add new skills to your creative toolbelt with our latest Software Bundle with awesome digital art and illustration courses from the experts at Skillademia. Learn how to draw and design original people, animals, and more like a pro with the &lt;em&gt;Character Design Course: Master Character Digital Illustration&lt;/em&gt; course, master the principles of drawing and sketching in Procreate with the &lt;em&gt;Procreate Course: Master Digital Illustration&lt;/em&gt; course, and more. Pay what you want and help support Make-A-Wish with your purchase!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#procreate"&gt;Procreate Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#adobeillustrator"&gt;Adobe Illustrator Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt10"&gt;Pay $10 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#canva"&gt;Canva Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#clipstudiopaint"&gt;Clip Studio Paint Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt20"&gt;Pay $20 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#characterdesign"&gt;Character Design Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pixelart"&gt;Pixel Art Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#comicbookcreation"&gt;Comic Book Creation Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="procreate"&gt;&lt;a id="procreate" href="https://youtu.be/8Ye