uad&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#snipersquad"&gt;Sniper Squad&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#tacticalsquad"&gt;Tactical Squad&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#valhallagate"&gt;Valhalla Gate&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vikingchurch"&gt;Viking Church&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vikingporthouse"&gt;Viking Port house&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vikingroundhouse"&gt;Viking Round House&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vikingwindmill"&gt;Viking Windmill&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#dwarfbattlerager"&gt;Dwarf Battlerager&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#mountaingiant"&gt;Mountain Giant&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#stormherald"&gt;Storm Herald&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#zealotbarbarian"&gt;Zealot Barbarian&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#orcberserker"&gt;Orc Berserker&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#minotaurwarrior"&gt;Minotaur Warrior&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#stormgiant"&gt;Storm Giant&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#valkyrie"&gt;Valkyrie&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#cart"&gt;Cart&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#gallows"&gt;Gallows&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bathtub"&gt;Bathtub&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bedset"&gt;Bed set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#woodencrane"&gt;Wooden Crane&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#storehouse_v1"&gt;Store House_v1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#storehouse_v2"&gt;Store House_v2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#treehouse"&gt;Tree House&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vikingfightingpit"&gt;Viking Fighting Pit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="animalcompanionpack_setof5"&gt;&lt;a id="animalcompanionpack_setof5"&gt;Animal Companion Pack - Set of 5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f4b0a4adf2220c0e7c903f766ea84cb9097ed2eb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2064e52b4371b31bf7be2ca4c58bebaa"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Animal Companion Pack gathers five faithful familiars—wolf, bear, panther, hawk and owl—each sculpted at crisp 32 mm heroic scale. Supplied in both pre‑supported and clean STL files, every creature is keyed to scenic bases and test‑printed on 8 K MSLA machines for plug‑and‑play success. Perfect as ranger beasts, druids’ wild‑shape options or painting projects, this set lets you populate a bestiary with a single download and a lifetime personal licence.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="frostgiant"&gt;&lt;a id="frostgiant"&gt;Frost Giant&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/fcbf39bfdb363a10eed1bbd8aab0cfa13c665ff1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=aa9986675c9909831f232413394489b9"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ice‑forged conqueror towering at 115 mm, wielding runic great‑sword and glacier shield. Snow drift base supplied.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="taverncounterset"&gt;&lt;a id="taverncounterset"&gt;Tavern Counter Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/cb5b89cc755840bc9e0b6abbfeb4175acee39fa7.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=570a4f9c22244896f2e901c8c675821e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bar counter, ale kegs, mugs, shelves and cash box for instant inn dressing. Pegged joins for sturdy assembly.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="weaponry"&gt;&lt;a id="weaponry"&gt;Weaponry&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/de33579a40446fc53cec77246e8a2f5050659cf6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=12bacf847d382ede08573fa4f3e9399c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Racks of swords, spears, maces and shields—perfect armoury scatter. Files arranged both single‑part and separated.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="tortureset"&gt;&lt;a id="tortureset"&gt;Torture Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ff7df1982a454704c1af085ffa7465884363e5c4.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=df5db316c5ccc2510be6675b1914bbc5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dungeon accessories including rack, iron maiden, shackles and branding brazier. Each prop pre‑supported.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="giantsandheroesbustcollection_setof8busts"&gt;&lt;a id="giantsandheroesbustcollection_setof8busts"&gt;Giants and Heroes Bust Collection - Set of 8 Busts&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/03851c03ff41e6e65f4535f72f008d5820fb9fef.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2beb6dee63d216f18ed8119d584b2fa4"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Eight epic busts—Frost Giant, Storm Herald, Mountain Giant, Zealot Barbarian, Orc Berserker, Minotaur Warrior, Dwarf Battlerager and Valkyrie—capture larger‑than‑life personalities in showcase scale. Each bust is hollowed, keyed and pre‑supported for resin efficiency while retaining razor‑sharp detail in skin, armour and braided hair. Ideal for display painting or campaign props, the collection comes with clean meshes, printer‑friendly wall thicknesses and a lifetime personal licence.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="abandonedbuildingspack_setof5"&gt;&lt;a id="abandonedbuildingspack_setof5"&gt;Abandoned Buildings Pack - Set of 5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6ebcccfc348d683b4a96aa9e8f9c75e06abd5aec.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4686c712be509ffb58598b44314c594f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Transform any tabletop into a forsaken hamlet with five modular ruins featuring shattered timber frames, cracked stone foundations and printable interiors. Walls cap at 120 mm to fit most resin vats, and each piece is hollowed with drain channels to save resin. Mix‑and‑match floor plates allow endless board configurations while keyed joins ensure easy assembly. Pre‑supported files plus unsupported masters give you complete control under The Master Forge lifetime licence.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="woodlandmonsters_setof3"&gt;&lt;a id="woodlandmonsters_setof3"&gt;Woodland Monsters - Set of 3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9ad44ef4d187cb132873d5af7f31ebddef4b230e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=08dd9c42e203736da6832321c3c09509"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This trio of sylvan terrors—Tree Ent, Vine Wraith and Bog Crawler—emerges from the forest with twisted bark textures and creeping roots. Sculpted for 32 mm encounters, the monsters stand 65–90 mm tall atop integrated scenic bases. Pre‑supported and unsupported files are included; each model prints in two to three keyed parts for painting access. Add them as boss fights, druid summons or terrain scatter with unlimited personal prints.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vikingraiderlongship"&gt;&lt;a id="vikingraiderlongship"&gt;Viking Raider Longship&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0547bc0632a73ea14eb695c30e0248961b9e2ea6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=eaf2bbdf8c623625daa2ca19974812b7"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A 10.5‑inch long drakkar brimming with Norse flavour: carved dragon prow, Viking shields, working oar ports and removable mast. The hull prints in segmented, keyed sections sized for mid‑size resin vats; interior planking is recessed for easy dry‑brushing. Optional stretcher bars let you convert to an on‑table terrain piece or a seaworthy gaming prop. Pre‑supported variants included—just slice, print, glue and set sail.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="campfiresceneset"&gt;&lt;a id="campfiresceneset"&gt;Campfire Scene Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5e1b4b9d629271e79559caa8eb7e2de5c10682f1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2a35c8f16b3e4a3bf89e43f5fa71927f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Complete campsite diorama featuring flickering‑log firepit, Ring‑of‑Stones base, bedrolls, cooking tripod, stewpots and scatter logs. Everything is scaled to 28–32 mm minis and provided in both print‑in‑place (all props on one plate) and standalone STL options. Pre‑supported files use minimal contact points to keep surfaces clean; hollowed logs reduce material. A one‑stop download for wilderness encounters and storytelling vignettes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="midgardserpentminiature"&gt;&lt;a id="midgardserpentminiature"&gt;Midgard Serpent Miniature&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ffdf1431220df40e73e2422bcbf304555717f755.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1c7288b2a7d650b53da11e8873a395b0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Coil the seas around your players with the Midgard Serpent: a 200 mm‑long leviathan curling over a rocky base. Supplied in six keyed, hollow parts and fully pre‑supported for large‑format resin printers, the sculpt showcases scale plates, horned frills and an open maw bursting with fangs. Unsupported masters and a prescaled 75 % version are included for smaller vats. Print once or a fleet—your lifetime licence never expires.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="birdmonk"&gt;&lt;a id="birdmonk"&gt;Bird Monk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3d8613741e3e2da991950255d5dc1e5d0096ac3f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d32c8ae16d9f48ed564beb3446b47c95"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Grace in motion: this avian martial‑artist stands poised on one talon, wind‑ruffled robes sweeping around feathered limbs. Designed for 32 mm play, the model arrives in two keyed parts with both pre‑supported and raw STL files. Perfect as an Aarakocra PC, NPC mentor or exotic boss encounter.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="paladinaasimar"&gt;&lt;a id="paladinaasimar"&gt;Paladin Aasimar&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7a200e8f1448a416578ddc92018ec05197c72c09.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5b5cede4d84b3427e40425dd351e0792"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Haloed champion clad in celestial plate, longsword raised in righteous challenge. Layered armour panels, angelic sigils and flowing cape all resolve crisply on consumer resin printers thanks to thin but sturdy supports. Includes alt‑helmeted head and separate shield arm for kit‑bashing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="firbolgcleric"&gt;&lt;a id="firbolgcleric"&gt;Firbolg Cleric&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ac39f2b9c87b7c2fcda6957193246843a36f1f54.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a0391729045541ca021942e7cd0064d5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Gentle forest giant wielding rune‑etched staff and crystal focus. Layered leaf‑cloak, carved totem accessories and a serene expression reward dedicated painters. Prints in three keyed sections, each pre‑supported and hollowed for resin efficiency.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="gnomebarbarian"&gt;&lt;a id="gnomebarbarian"&gt;Gnome Barbarian&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/22430c461b9304a86f99e9198ffa8c219f704445.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=cc28bfaa29a1db8a3a60f9b2179eb5cc"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Don’t judge his size—this ferocious gnome swings a double‑headed axe as big as he is. Dynamic overhead strike pose, fur‑mantle texture and braided beard detail guaranteed to hold paint washes. Pre‑supported STL plus unsupported master included.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="hobgoblinartificer"&gt;&lt;a id="hobgoblinartificer"&gt;Hobgoblin Artificer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/598ef7b84cdb5b80c747810bc714d65ee5cbc6cd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=41c503bdac240547535bb6039e98c1e6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Armoured tinkerer with arc‑pistol and modular backpack forge. Mechanical limbs, tool pouches and glowing rune‑cores make great NMM or OSL practice. Model splits at waist and backpack for easy airbrushing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="kenkurogue"&gt;&lt;a id="kenkurogue"&gt;Kenku Rogue&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0992389818040ab8ff13a0baac0b55fbe446e0df.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=80a70eb5de5a2e6adfce7673ca7ef3cf"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Knife‑wielding corvid skulker in layered leathers. Feather textures recessed for sharp prints; cloak underside hollowed to save resin. Choice of hood‑up or hood‑down head sculpts in the zip.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="halforcmerchant"&gt;&lt;a id="halforcmerchant"&gt;Half Orc Merchant&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4b5ef052a1302aaca09cba80ba1b8e526e411bdd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=12f25009c8e475c9d634bf7b8a43bd86"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;World‑weary trader hefting cargo crate and ledger, ideal as quest‑giver NPC. Robust folds, coin‑pouch details and removable display base included.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="halflingthief"&gt;&lt;a id="halflingthief"&gt;Halfling Thief&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f42971842db3a3683825a85e97534a6f56167ff0.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5d3ceb641918698ba72adda8080ba8b0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Clever burglar mid‑sprint with loot bag and lock‑picks. Supported at just 28 mm tall yet retains crisp facial features; unsupported file supplied for custom scaling.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lizardfolkranger"&gt;&lt;a id="lizardfolkranger"&gt;Lizardfolk Ranger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e636b07b3830480e4a1342390e0a8602b25fe56a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4f399f5736c775c2242456023302828d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Scale‑armoured hunter drawing recurve bow, quiver of bone‑fletched arrows, optional spear arm. Split across torso and tail for support‑free interior surfaces.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="plaguedoctor"&gt;&lt;a id="plaguedoctor"&gt;Plague Doctor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5273031a274cb86032157ebb8b18b9e1ffcee075.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b07227d1c49f0d1049cdb6abb0cd3718"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dark‑age medic gripping torch and apothecary satchel. Beak mask, stitched leathers and potion vials textured for contrast. Includes alt hand with scalpel for horror scenarios.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="warforgedfighter"&gt;&lt;a id="warforgedfighter"&gt;Warforged Fighter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3006a82e6d0be77f99053ca37ff8ef3def35564b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e2eceec3fa336c16d1866f5730ed643f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Arcane‑steel construct advancing with greatsword. Interlocking plate segments, glowing‑core chest and gear‑motif base: perfect for washes and edge highlights.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="changelingspy"&gt;&lt;a id="changelingspy"&gt;Changeling Spy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d35fcada2210ceec40fca194ecf35ff5b9f0afaf.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=df4fc065b3784243670d8582342dce2f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shapeshifter mid‑transition: half‑masked face and morphing limbs. Optional fully revealed and fully disguised heads provided.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="dragonbornknight"&gt;&lt;a id="dragonbornknight"&gt;Dragonborn Knight&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/bf29ba0ab1ef4293abde3dbd5737e833460b7a89.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0d8a7c3efa23efe0a73c4ff19f01c347"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Scaled paladin in drake‑themed armour, tower shield and flame‑engraved longsword. Prints in four keyed pieces; horns reinforced with internal pegs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="dwarfwizard"&gt;&lt;a id="dwarfwizard"&gt;Dwarf Wizard&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/52f80365225bfbe353cc63a2df62e447dce6a356.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=eecc6a7fc197c6f6a594791c2a04c113"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Runesmith sage clutching spellbook and rune‑hammer. Cloak embossed with Khazad script; separate smoke‑spell effect included.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="elfarcher_tmf"&gt;&lt;a id="elfarcher_tmf"&gt;Elf Archer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/016f63c8079d2b8e96b41115cc7faf9c60b8c6d8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1b052fe0a8a974c4d61327ebcb2f3e2f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Longbow champion in flowing leafmail drawing fletched arrow. Comes with quiver‑on‑hip and quiver‑on‑back variants.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="drowassassin"&gt;&lt;a id="drowassassin"&gt;Drow Assassin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a26bf00495b96b3c55479830688b262544a9f1f5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d647daebb91fb0c354686ceba850c653"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shadow‑stalker balanced on stalagmite, dual poisoned daggers ready. Includes alt posing arm with hand‑crossbow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="halfelfqueen"&gt;&lt;a id="halfelfqueen"&gt;Half Elf Queen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7a30eec7087ec3e167c89c325862fa22b2202fcc.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=80206df09592db785bfa0dc5c4a7cc48"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Regal sovereign on gem‑inlaid base, sceptre raised. Flowing gown drapes designed for clean support removal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="gnomewarlock"&gt;&lt;a id="gnomewarlock"&gt;Gnome Warlock&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/247fd78b61d642b150dc835f2b086338d837bdec.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0b42b829ce79330088a42ac8b7a796a4"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Arcane prodigy casting eldritch blast; swirling energy effect prints in transparent resin beautifully.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="humanking"&gt;&lt;a id="humanking"&gt;Human King&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/767dd0a835ae52c6b9ba43f22f67b1099c390a27.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c08649b1c170b10f72debe47fc09a92b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stalwart monarch on lion‑carved throne base. Throne provided as separate STL for standalone terrain use.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="humandemonhunter"&gt;&lt;a id="humandemonhunter"&gt;Human Demon Hunter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4bfb934bf085cc4cec9db7299ae6d1ba65cb48c6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a17569c91247cab52dbdea00ea4c6ff6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Leather‑clad hunter brandishing rune‑pistol and silvered blade, dynamic trench‑coat swirl ideal for OSL.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="infiltrationsquad"&gt;&lt;a id="infiltrationsquad"&gt;Infiltration Squad&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3a81669ee06283781e39e58a3e75267a7333be49.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9c37197718bf07f54ac56b14a9972b0a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Five covert‑ops Brokk‑r troops with suppressors, hacking rigs and stealth packs. Modular heads and weapon options, fully pre‑supported and hollowed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="demolitionsquad"&gt;&lt;a id="demolitionsquad"&gt;Demolition Squad&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/cd6899a381f332f7457191038fdb788ee062cf99.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=12f3cf42fa73d07019771526e9b93883"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Explosive experts with breacher shields, remote charges and wrist‑fuse igniters. Modelled smoke plume effect supplied separately.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="heavyassaultsquad"&gt;&lt;a id="heavyassaultsquad"&gt;Heavy Assault Squad&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d04a45681e56bb444fcac7dd4f3e046d4dbf7c99.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a58c24d55a34881cc8a7ed73ddc46aff"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Armour‑plated juggernauts wielding rotary cannons and heat shields. Prints flawlessly at 0.03 mm layers; keyed arm sockets for pose swaps.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="snipersquad"&gt;&lt;a id="snipersquad"&gt;Sniper Squad&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/bee4b32e8b0fc01192c5b6f9225da6afb4d64add.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=96bd2a38d80bec1c5e3c60dd033075f0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Long‑range marksmen with anti‑materiel rifles and deployable camo cloaks. Optional bipod‑down parts included.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="tacticalsquad"&gt;&lt;a id="tacticalsquad"&gt;Tactical Squad&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/26f260e0483781e5769fce61d1470f553455f87d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=bef1d95ef912a797ff7cd917949efe41"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Core infantry unit with modular rifles, axes and banner. Squad leader has swap‑out head and power‑fist options.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="valhallagate"&gt;&lt;a id="valhallagate"&gt;Valhalla Gate&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9023bb3f645963d3b3ec43c8a1afce538a37ad6a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d97de180d3d04990e740b91e61f495a6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Grand portal crowned with rune‑arch and shield murals, scaled for 28–32 mm minis. Double doors are separate, printable pieces.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vikingchurch"&gt;&lt;a id="vikingchurch"&gt;Viking Church&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/519cc87031188913a252a954dc7617b37a01247a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6633562bb648dbae476d44700ece0106"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stave‑style sanctuary complete with removable roof and interior pews. Prints in sectional slices for any consumer resin printer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vikingporthouse"&gt;&lt;a id="vikingporthouse"&gt;Viking Port house&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a2717fd5c3e7e7ee4627c774a5e6787f649a0cda.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7406dea4af3c373780c909755e761b2b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Waterside warehouse with dock posts and cargo stacks. Modular pier extension lets you build full harbour scenes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vikingroundhouse"&gt;&lt;a id="vikingroundhouse"&gt;Viking Round House&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/bbab7245869b5e9e2a74e381bf73c6b19548ddc4.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9848bc3816037779b11c06e714587e0d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Residential hut featuring timber‑plank walls, thatch roof and functional doorway. Roof halves removable for interior access.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vikingwindmill"&gt;&lt;a id="vikingwindmill"&gt;Viking Windmill&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8930e0f90a34531c9eb7e639e86f8e426aa1e935.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d0d4685adae488ef487eac07271a37e0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Rotating mill blades supplied on printable axle; stone base and timber upper storey print separately.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="dwarfbattlerager"&gt;&lt;a id="dwarfbattlerager"&gt;Dwarf Battlerager&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/33e34f0296afcf95f83a0575f6d4852d183e85a6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4bdacc500f1d2ca75e174fde4365bd1d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Armoured berserker bristling with spike plates, roaring mid‑charge. Optional helmeted head and twin‑axe arms.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="mountaingiant"&gt;&lt;a id="mountaingiant"&gt;Mountain Giant&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3b0dc25b8a52c352115346bf69055203c5a9a7f0.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=32f87573adda784b70ea88c44b76a154"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Looming 130 mm titan hefting boulder club; skin etched with cliff‑face cracks. Supported and hollowed for safe curing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="stormherald"&gt;&lt;a id="stormherald"&gt;Storm Herald&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0b0bf8472b268c3d691b71e11919646e5d608a9b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=268aa2ee5e0bad4a5d42647eef6cf430"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Storm‑charged warrior with lightning‑wreathed hammer and billowing cape. Separate lightning effect prints in clear resin.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="zealotbarbarian"&gt;&lt;a id="zealotbarbarian"&gt;Zealot Barbarian&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2887a625648141a94af44d06b3727ebc7caa2f26.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=65edfda58590c240c3002713f4403ffb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bare‑chested fanatic swinging twin great‑axes. Includes optional fur cloak and alternate shouting head.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="orcberserker"&gt;&lt;a id="orcberserker"&gt;Orc Berserker&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e582dee6e702e8f76b4644efecbc7f601f4fb6ea.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2891228d794cf2bc2230030900df48fe"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Savage orc mid‑leap, cleaver raised high. Base features shattered shields and skulls for narrative impact.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="minotaurwarrior"&gt;&lt;a id="minotaurwarrior"&gt;Minotaur Warrior&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/b74dd9ac7c633744513d0da4cc2feace27a39c09.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=34500a81d4b3be4bb70e47f829fbafee"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Horned labyrinth guardian gripping double‑bladed greataxe. Musculature and fur maps reward dry‑brushing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="stormgiant"&gt;&lt;a id="stormgiant"&gt;Storm Giant&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5d72f2fdd7dde4242c4a1dce2971c8631ca05787.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a0b9aec678eab395fac5cff7187e6122"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sky‑borne monarch cloaked in thundercloud cape, trident crackling with energy. Prints in 9 keyed parts for easy painting.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="valkyrie"&gt;&lt;a id="valkyrie"&gt;Valkyrie&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f4613bd553de8bf562cf53e9f5c32f1e026eb461.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=601c001375c1e644172909b68d1ed59b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Winged shield‑maiden descending with spear and round shield. Optional helmet plume and scenic rock base parts.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cart"&gt;&lt;a id="cart"&gt;Cart&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/414d04ab5f450a43611999e22136bf942153cd8f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1e3561618fcc447d8b51dde0d8969ced"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sturdy two‑wheeled cart with removable yoke and cargo bundle scatter. Prints support‑free on FDM or resin machines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="gallows"&gt;&lt;a id="gallows"&gt;Gallows&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3e791352764e7f2c865b35b08512eb39f8636460.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6ceb8ea97dac7c8d0aeb5e30358b632c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Grim wooden gallows with working trap‑door platform and rope piece. Ideal for frontier towns or horror scenarios.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="bathtub"&gt;&lt;a id="bathtub"&gt;Bathtub&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/efdf59e00c819af73433cbd06d9268fd19a4c0b2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=fe20aaf63c316488f91b24ec7dfeafc8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Claw‑foot tub, stack of towels, soap dish and splash insert—everything you need for a medieval bathhouse scene.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="bedset"&gt;&lt;a id="bedset"&gt;Bed set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c6961a48a2c9815d832bc49f9b49c67d5f8f0c66.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=abc98e7b22bb239a07678867ed237eb4"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Carved four‑poster bed with draped curtains, pillow stack and folded quilt. Prints in two hollow halves.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="woodencrane"&gt;&lt;a id="woodencrane"&gt;Wooden Crane&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/afb5ec318338ea019fb8f127804c5b74a73c4c65.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=57555fd4198aefd4b90208451f4fe86a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Functional dockside crane with winch gear and hanging cargo net. Joints engineered to glue flush or pin.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="storehouse_v1"&gt;&lt;a id="storehouse_v1"&gt;Store House_v1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/445054516e71e41a1808e58c306c83469ce96c90.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c4c3de6e885440ddbca267382c126562"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Two‑storey timber warehouse with ladder, hatch and hinged doors. Floors slot in without glue for playable interiors.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="storehouse_v2"&gt;&lt;a id="storehouse_v2"&gt;Store House_v2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/870af5e1d19683cdf4f943d0da6c12a83891a450.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=38fb496d9088d7236167eb311a85334e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alternate stone‑foundation storehouse with raised loading dock and detachable roof. Prints in sectional pieces.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="treehouse"&gt;&lt;a id="treehouse"&gt;Tree House&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/dc74f3cb03b9108135020f72ac87b33b973f0211.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e350190af4bce62a0b1b4cb28c876358"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Elevated woodland dwelling with rope bridge segment, hollow trunk interior and lookout deck. Modular stilts fit any terrain board.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vikingfightingpit"&gt;&lt;a id="vikingfightingpit"&gt;Viking Fighting Pit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5e4bfc5b25f3c893072a7323db810efd15be825a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e104a5c907ec80584e6609539961c1a9"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sunken arena with timber palisade, spectator stands and bone‑strewn floor. Perfect for gladiator side‑quests.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
