      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0e2db395653c286297d3055c2c9c21e5f2ba8d23.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=079af343a8e2a182aece7b24741c319c"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/af57c475abb0422b125554556da02d412254b739.png?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=d1302797e8f1e608b94ee9921a7c61b8"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Sweet tunes from hot games  &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get the sweetest tracks from the hottest games with the Materia Collective Original Soundtrack Bundle! Need to set some tunes on and chill? We’ve got you covered with the &lt;em&gt;Celeste Original Soundtrack&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Superliminal Original Soundtrack&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Shadows Over Loathing Original Soundtrack&lt;/em&gt;, and more atmospheric, sensational tracks. Bring your day-to-day soundtrack to life with premium music and help support Make-A-Wish with your purchase.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;a style="color:#EF9741"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;The titles in this bundle are original soundtracks and not to be used in other works.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#undertaleoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;UNDERTALE Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pizzatoweroriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Pizza Tower Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#owlboyoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Owlboy Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt8"&gt;Pay $8 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#westofloathingoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;West of Loathing Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#grimeoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;GRIME Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#celesteoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Celeste Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#mossoriginalgamesoundtrack"&gt;Moss (Original Game Soundtrack)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#deltarunechapter1ost"&gt;DELTARUNE Chapter 1 OST&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt13"&gt;Pay $13 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#returnoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Return Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#shadowsoverloathingoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Shadows Over Loathing Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#superliminaloriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Superliminal Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#nostraightroadsoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;No Straight Roads Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#spookysjumpscaremansionoriginalgamesoundtrack"&gt;Spooky's Jump Scare Mansion Original Game Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#necrobaristaoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Necrobarista Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#deltarunechapter2ost"&gt;DELTARUNE Chapter 2 OST&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="undertaleoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;&lt;a id="undertaleoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;UNDERTALE Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/22f5c36a04f5f9797fa0e2e811aa74a388977b63.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7a90a57a9b359b20e0a1b087b427aafb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Soundtrack to UNDERTALE.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pizzatoweroriginalsoundtrack"&gt;&lt;a id="pizzatoweroriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Pizza Tower Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c4158baf5baff36a40f5700f5f574a4f846160c9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a43a1403b2a2fb047468aae162a91b4e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate Pizza Music! Groove to the music of Pizza Tower, with over 70 hits to move your butt to!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="owlboyoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;&lt;a id="owlboyoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Owlboy Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/97848205c1620fb2d3082a2d14dea9fa6358ad07.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d030939d3bf2c1ff3d21b042abde3bdc"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Official Soundtrack for Owlboy. Owlboy was developed by D-Pad Studio and is currently available on PC. All music composed and produced by Jonathan Geer.&lt;h2 id="bt8"&gt;Pay $8 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="westofloathingoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;&lt;a id="westofloathingoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;West of Loathing Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1bd836419fa8288a8ea4a46009acbccbafa431cb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e34a4ac8e8cea8096f6c18f904378d13"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;If yer fixin' fer a real hootenanny of a toe-tapper, this might be jus' the ear-vittles what fer to cure what ails ya! Saddle up for a rootin'-tootin' humdinger of a god I can't do this. West of Loathing is an RPG about cowboy stick figures and I did the music for it.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is that music.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="grimeoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;&lt;a id="grimeoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;GRIME Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/b2376b4e766893f058dc79245395119a8f43c5d7.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c08f45856f9ef25e2b1e091b317a294d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;From veteran UK composer Alex Roe, GRIME (Original Game Soundtrack) features a vast palette of dark fantasy and electronic sounds dressing up powerful melodies that represent the protagonist's incredible force of nature against the world.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="celesteoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;&lt;a id="celesteoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Celeste Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0cd4c8b8c56fa9fe8edbd6a0abe9e08ddb43f0df.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e423ef5b9a51362d82dc6d1e1c3e3e79"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Original soundtrack for the game Celeste by Maddy, Noel, Amora, Pedro, Lena, Kevin &amp;amp; friends!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="mossoriginalgamesoundtrack"&gt;&lt;a id="mossoriginalgamesoundtrack"&gt;Moss (Original Game Soundtrack)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ff71cd50fe72a0fa5e1bf888094ecd68a14fd4c8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c936ce8d69421f4bc98548176535eedd"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A melodic and playful adventure score conveys Quill's story in Moss from her perspective by employing small and intimate-sounding instruments – flute, oboe, Celtic harp, English hammered dulcimer, acoustic guitar, and classical violin – all composed, arranged and produced in a pastoral soundscape with enchanting Waltz-esque flair.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="deltarunechapter1ost"&gt;&lt;a id="deltarunechapter1ost"&gt;DELTARUNE Chapter 1 OST&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2f53024aa1455a16f363b88f8422de040afb2113.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e4254b86efeb5bf5671dabe7c82cdbae"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;DELTARUNE Chapter 1 OST&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is the official soundtrack for the first chapter of Deltarune.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt13"&gt;Pay $13 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="returnoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;&lt;a id="returnoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Return Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/75e1eea6230ca36e5cf9737e9ba7db51c6c41572.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f8b7e536e69f118452883860f77cbff1"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Return is an art driven, side-scrolling adventure set in the apocalyptic rebirth of your home planet, where your only hope of survival is to explore the unfamiliar landscape.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Many thanks to Jesse at Dead Unicorn Studios for allowing me to create the soundtrack and sound design of the beautiful project!!!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="shadowsoverloathingoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;&lt;a id="shadowsoverloathingoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Shadows Over Loathing Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c659430f02b4eccc4a8e12b8f3b68df409ec426f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5c993122ff301e7603e70c4f41b8cb5e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Do you yearn for the music of the void, as it yearns for you? Does some dark part of your mind–slumbering, and yet . . . awakened–pine to stare into the creeping, grinning blackness between the stars and feel its infinite dirge pour down upon you, like liquid into a vessel that knows not what it holds? Does your very being vibrate with the need to hear–truly hear–the coiling, undulating counterpoint of the Sound That Should Not Be? To feel its chattering, gnashing song course through your body, your brain bursting like overripe fruit as it twists you, transcending, into a form capable, at last, of joining it's horrifying chorus?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;No? Ok, whew. Like, honestly?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;That's great.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;I really don't think I had a shot at living up to all that. What I can present you with is this; the soundtrack to Shadows Over Loathing. It can't smush your brain like an old banana or whatever that was, but it does provide you with all of your favorite tunes from the eldritch horror/comedy game. Featuring some wildly talented performers and just the right amount of creepy vibes. Maybe not enough to make you want to stare directly into the Abyss Behind The Eyes Of The World, but maybe enough to make you want to kind of glance at it? Like from across a room, at a party or something. Flirty, even.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="superliminaloriginalsoundtrack"&gt;&lt;a id="superliminaloriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Superliminal Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f0607825e543686bc3a3d023de007d3e0296093f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=14246e6e427a017ec9dbbe9a0cf498bd"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Treat yourself with our safe and effective Superliminal dream therapy soundtrack, expertly selected by trained SumnaSculpt technician and composer Matt Christensen to make your dreams come true. Relax to the dulcet tones of our soothing jazz piano then thrill to the hybrid electronic beats before finally resolving all your dilemmas as we lead you through your dream back to reality. All tracks freshly mixed and mastered for pure listening pleasure.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="nostraightroadsoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;&lt;a id="nostraightroadsoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;No Straight Roads Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/92a885ae5c7444694c3de62466a1c63de54ce9e3.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=dd536121b7e9d36364ff27643bbdebfc"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Take back Vinyl City - with rock! Embark on a music-based action-adventure as indie rock band members Mayday &amp;amp; Zuke and lead a musical revolution against EDM empire No Straight Roads. After being unfairly rejected in their audition to join No Straight Roads, Mayday &amp;amp; Zuke uncover the evil intentions behind the NSR empire. It’s now down to them to save their city from corruption. Enjoy fast &amp;amp; frenetic combat with a musical twist as these two aspiring rock artists fight back with the power of music!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="spookysjumpscaremansionoriginalgamesoundtrack"&gt;&lt;a id="spookysjumpscaremansionoriginalgamesoundtrack"&gt;Spooky's Jump Scare Mansion Original Game Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/645b1d721ad58aaf65d4e76585e23d92252eef49.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4279720a965673eefac4753d8b3daf28"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;“Hello, I am Spooky. And this is my home. Can you, humble player, make it through one thousand rooms?”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Anyway jus—just go listen to the album…&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="necrobaristaoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;&lt;a id="necrobaristaoriginalsoundtrack"&gt;Necrobarista Original Soundtrack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c69993d97913d01c7a3eb3808593fe474fc103a6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f8c89745ad72625e036d45f74d441714"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;In a back-alley cafe, the dead are granted one last night to mingle with the living. Necrobarista follows a dynamic and diverse cast of characters as they navigate Melbourne's hipstery coffee culture, the questionable ethics of necromancy, and the process of letting go. Inspired equally by film and anime, Necrobarista is a unique take on the visual novel medium.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="deltarunechapter2ost"&gt;&lt;a id="deltarunechapter2ost"&gt;DELTARUNE Chapter 2 OST&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5d1da552684fe4c8eb2d195d0bc8717c18d8aff8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=46a5b7d3e3cf9118c489b3a3ac62822c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;DELTARUNE Chapter 2 OST is the official soundtrack for the second chapter of Deltarune.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
